Class GraphImpl<T>

java.lang.Object
ie.ucd.csnl.comp47500.implementation.GraphImpl<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the vertex data
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
SocialNetworkGraph
public class GraphImpl<T> extends Object implements Graph<T>
Implements the GraphInterface using an adjacency list to manage vertices and edges. This class provides a concrete implementation of a graph that can handle any type of data in vertices.
